detail.name: Zamasu : Fused
detail.effect: [On Play]  If you have 7 or fewer cards in your hand, choose up to 1 <Zamasu : Fused> in your Leader Area or Battle Area and it gets +5000 power until the end of your opponent's next turn.

detail.name: ザマス：合体
detail.effect: 【登場時】自分の手札が7枚以下の場合、自分のリーダーの「ザマス：合体」か自分のバトルエリアの「ザマス：合体」1枚までを選び、次の相手のターン終了時まで、パワー+5000。
